{"tid":2229220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西貢潛水男失蹤兩日 今尋回屍體","createTime":"2020-10-04T08:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T13:50:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"582a42ed55be7bef9ce8d5ed41c6104c8a33d4a4","tid":2229220,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:27:32.000Z","msg":"一名33歲姓黃男子，本月2日在西貢海下對開約300米海面浮潛，其間與友人失聯，友人懷疑他遇溺，報警求助。警方接獲報案後，連日來聯同多個部門到場搜救，但一直未有發現。警方、消防、海事處及飛行服務隊，今日（4日）繼續到場搜救，於今晨約11時在西貢海下串螺角咀發現黃男，人員將他救起後，黃現場被證實死亡，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201004/NTIXJSDAKRDJNMJAKWP423MDYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201004%2FNTIXJSDAKRDJNMJAKWP423MDYQ%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=569afaa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201004%2FNTIXJSDAKRDJNMJAKWP423MDYQ%2F&h=0d699554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201004/NTIXJSDAKRDJNMJAKWP423MDYQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f5c6c2d404c7ab7046584dbfd710b8a665c8ec15","tid":2229220,"uid":53666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"搵得返算唔錯"},{"pid":"92b1ccb6f7e74e5a46a4040590948608cc30ef1f","tid":2229220,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d224f7abc311949658355f933e8bd78dc11938fb","tid":2229220,"uid":84830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"rip<br />\n注意安全"},{"pid":"2e7d160ee028224781148b44a7e2c97591a1dde3","tid":2229220,"uid":193077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"去左龍宮？"},{"pid":"2fb32009251c57d2a7d0d77a5a05ec9e5d086ab7","tid":2229220,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:41:55.000Z","msg":"300米？ wtf"},{"pid":"9107184be2d09d707ee155747c0064d09